		{
			dependencies: ["t100000000000012"]
			description: [
				"The MekaSuit is Mekanism's endgame powered armor. Each piece has built-in modules for flight, auto-feeding, radiation shielding, and more."
				""
				"Craft and install modules via the Modification Station. A fully kitted MekaSuit rivals Creative-mode power. It requires massive energy and resources — a true pack capstone."
			]
