		{
			dependencies: ["t100000000000014"]
			description: [
				"The Charger uses energy to convert Certus Quartz into Charged Certus Quartz. You need Charged Certus to craft Fluix Crystals — a key AE2 material."
				""
				"Power it with any FE source (a Mekanism generator works great). Throw Charged Certus + Nether Quartz + Redstone into water to create Fluix."
