		{
			dependencies: ["t100000000000015"]
			description: [
				"The Inscriber stamps raw materials into circuits using Press plates. You need four presses: Logic, Calculation, Engineering, and Silicon."
				""
				"Find presses in Meteorites (use a Meteorite Compass to locate them). Each press is reusable. Circuits are needed for every AE2 machine and storage component."
