		{
			dependencies: ["t100000000000016"]
			description: [
				"The ME Controller is the brain of your AE2 network. It provides channels (up to 32 per face) that allow devices to communicate."
				""
				"Without a Controller, you are limited to 8 devices total. Place it centrally and run ME cables outward to your terminals, drives, and crafting setup."
