			description: [
				"The ME Drive holds Storage Cells that digitally store thousands of item types. Insert cells (1k, 4k, 16k, 64k) into the drive to add capacity."
				""
				"Each cell stores a limited number of item types and total count. Use multiple drives or higher-tier cells as your collection grows. This replaces rooms of chests."
