			description: [
				"The Coke Oven is a 3x3x3 multiblock that slowly converts Coal into Coal Cite and Creosote Oil. Coal Coke burns twice as long and is needed for the Blast Furnace."
				""
				"Build it from Coke Bricks (made from Clay and Sandstone). Creosote Oil is used to make Treated Wood, IE's core building material. Build two ovens to keep up with demand."
